reviewText: Again, another look into the ambition and tenacity these young men have to go through such a grueling program. Kudo's to all the SEALs and all military persons, men and women who put their lives on the line for freedom!

Originally thought I was ordering the PBS documentary (same title, ASIN: B00O9ZSKIQ). I'd already seen all but one of the episodes on YouTube, but decided to add this to my DVD collection. Thanks to all our Armed Forces personnel who volunteer to serve. They're some of the most under appreciated (and under paid) people I know. Thanks also to their families, as a former "Air Force Brat" I know what it's like being moved around every 3 or 4 years. Make sure you let them know that they're appreciated! God Bless the USA!
I have not watched all of it.  But what I have seen is good.  I ordered 2 of the same by mistake.
